{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.026.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.027.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Jotham, roi de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. 2 R 15:32-38. Pr 21:29. 3 Jn 12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Jotham avait vingt-cinq ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna seize ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Jeruscha, fille de Tsadok.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.2","name":"2 Chroniques 27:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.26.23","name":"2 Chroniques 26:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.26.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.027.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.027.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, enti\u00e8rement comme avait fait Ozias, son p\u00e8re. Seulement, il n\u2019entra point dans le temple de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Toutefois, le peuple se corrompait encore.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.3","name":"2 Chroniques 27:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.1","name":"2 Chroniques 27:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.027.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.027.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Jotham b\u00e2tit la porte sup\u00e9rieure de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il fit beaucoup de constructions sur les murs de la colline.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.4","name":"2 Chroniques 27:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.2","name":"2 Chroniques 27:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.027.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.027.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il b\u00e2tit des villes dans la montagne de Juda, et des ch\u00e2teaux et des tours dans les bois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.5","name":"2 Chroniques 27:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.3","name":"2 Chroniques 27:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.027.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.027.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il fut en guerre avec le roi des fils d\u2019Ammon, et il l\u2019emporta sur eux. Les fils d\u2019Ammon lui donn\u00e8rent cette ann\u00e9e-l\u00e0 cent talents d\u2019argent, dix mille cors de froment, et dix mille d\u2019orge; et ils lui en pay\u00e8rent autant la seconde ann\u00e9e et la troisi\u00e8me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.6","name":"2 Chroniques 27:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.4","name":"2 Chroniques 27:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.027.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.027.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Jotham devint puissant, parce qu\u2019il affermit ses voies devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.7","name":"2 Chroniques 27:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.5","name":"2 Chroniques 27:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.027.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.027.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Jotham, toutes ses guerres, et tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, cela est \u00e9crit dans le livre des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.8","name":"2 Chroniques 27:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.6","name":"2 Chroniques 27:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.027.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.027.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il avait vingt-cinq ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna seize ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.9","name":"2 Chroniques 27:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.7","name":"2 Chroniques 27:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 27:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.027.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.028.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.27.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Jotham se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et on l\u2019enterra dans la ville de David. Et Achaz, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27","name":"2 Chroniques 27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.28.1","name":"2 Chroniques 28:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.28.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.27.8","name":"2 Chroniques 27:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.27.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb5d3a9d1.47828915');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5d3a9d1.47828915\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb5d3a9d1.47828915","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fu